Package: ggsequence
Title: Geoms and stats for displaying protein sequences using ggplot2
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: person("Hiren", "Joshi", email = "ggsequence@glycocode.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Aligns protein sequences and produces plots that can be further annotated with extra data such as PTMs
